Package org.rapla.mobile.android.os

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectToServerAsyncTask
    This class asyncronously connects to the Rapla server by using another AsyncTask.
    ConnectToServerBackgroundAsyncTask
    This class contains the logic for connecting to the Rapla server.
    LoadAllocatablesAsyncTask
    This class asynchronously loads allocatables and assignes them to the list view UI.
    LoadAppointmentsAsyncTask
    This class asynchronously loads allocatables for the given reservation and assignes them to the list view UI.
    LoadUserCalendarsAsyncTask
    This class asyncronously loads all calendars assigned to the currently logged in user and assigned them to the given list view.
